ivardefs.name: ifMatch
ivardefs.desc: Only perform the operation if the Etag value matches. For more information, see the API section ["Managing Resource Contention"](http.html#concurrency).

ivardefs.name: ifModifiedSince
ivardefs.desc: Only perform the operation if the last updated date matches. See the API documentation for ["Conditional Read"](http.html#cread).

ivardefs.name: ifNoneExist

ivardefs.name: ifNoneMatch
ivardefs.desc: If the ETag values match, return a 304 Not Modified status. See the API documentation for ["Conditional Read"](http.html#cread).

ivardefs.name: method
ivardefs.desc: The HTTP verb for this entry in either a change history, or a transaction/ transaction response.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: The URL for this entry, relative to the root (the address to which the request is posted).

properties.desc: Additional information about how this entry should be processed as part of a transaction.
